<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/50019261-lean-g-a"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1476500629i/50019261._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
