        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3986059357" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18183559295927375151">I didn&apos;t expect high. It was a part of my essay writing course. I wrote an assignment on it. I was surprised how well developed this novella was in terms of plot and writing. The flow was splendid. Nothing felt unbelievable. Everything fell in piece like it should have while giving me a lot of suspense and interest in seeing what happens next. Fascinating part is, it&apos;s not a mystery, but it raised a lot of questions in me.</span>
  <span id="freeText18183559295927375151" style="display:none">I didn't expect high. It was a part of my essay writing course. I wrote an assignment on it. I was surprised how well developed this novella was in terms of plot and writing. The flow was splendid. Nothing felt unbelievable. Everything fell in piece like it should have while giving me a lot of suspense and interest in seeing what happens next. Fascinating part is, it's not a mystery, but it raised a lot of questions in me.</span>
