ve escaped. But I am still imprisoned.<br><br>Trapped:<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1440439530i/15975439._SX540_.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"></span>
